headline: What Analyst Projections for Key Metrics Reveal About Allegion (ALLE) Q3 Earnings
summary: Beyond analysts' top-and-bottom-line estimates for Allegion (ALLE), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended September 2025.
